-HEY! THAT'S MY HARMONICA.

11:25.249 --> 11:28.426
-OH, SORRY, I WAS
LOOKING FOR YOU.

11:30.777 --> 11:32.953
YOU DROPPED IT WHEN YOU WERE
RUNNING AWAY FROM THE TRUCK.

11:33.605 --> 11:34.519
HERE.

11:35.564 --> 11:37.261
-YOU GOT YOUR SPIT ALL OVER IT.

11:37.392 --> 11:39.524
-OH, SORRY.

11:42.179 --> 11:43.833
YOU KNOW HOW TO PLAY IT?

11:43.964 --> 11:47.141
-NO. JUST LIKE THE WAY
YOU CAN HEAR YOURSELF BREATHE.

11:48.185 --> 11:54.017
[HARMONICA MUSIC]

11:55.758 --> 11:56.672
-WHATCHA WRITING ABOUT?

11:57.760 --> 11:58.848
-WHAT JUST HAPPENED.

11:59.588 --> 12:00.502
-OH, LIKE A DIARY.

12:00.632 --> 12:01.764
-A JOURNAL.

12:02.765 --> 12:03.723
ME AND MY MOM SHARE IT.

12:17.388 --> 12:20.348
-SO, DID YOU WRITE ABOUT WHY

12:20.478 --> 12:22.437
YOU STOLE THAT STUFF BACK THERE?

12:22.567 --> 12:24.787
-I PAID IN ADVANCE
AND HE FORGOT, OKAY?

12:26.049 --> 12:28.356
HEY, HE'S THE ONE WHO
RIPPED ME OFF MY CHANGE,

12:28.486 --> 12:30.097
AND THAT WAS ALL
THE MONEY I HAD.

12:30.227 --> 12:31.620
WHAT ARE YOU STARING AT?

12:31.751 --> 12:33.100
-UH, YOU HAVE SOME
CHOCOLATE RIGHT HERE.

12:43.153 --> 12:43.937
YOU USE MAKEUP?

12:44.067 --> 12:45.329
-SOMETIMES.

12:49.203 --> 12:51.727
MY NAME'S CHARLIE,
WHAT'S YOURS?

12:51.858 --> 12:53.163
-HOBIE.

12:54.121 --> 12:57.689
-LISTEN, HOBIE, I GOTTA GET TO
WORK AND EARNIN' SOME MONEY.

12:57.820 --> 12:58.734
-YOU HAVE A JOB?

13:00.040 --> 13:01.084
-SORTA.

13:01.693 --> 13:03.695
HERE, PLAY THIS.

13:04.479 --> 13:05.828
-I DON'T KNOW HOW.

13:06.350 --> 13:08.352
-IT DOESN'T MATTER, JUST DO
LIKE YOU WERE DOING BEFORE.

13:08.483 --> 13:11.094
YOU KNOW, BLOW OUT AND SUCK IN.

13:11.225 --> 13:13.575
[HARMONICA MUSIC]
MOVE IT SIDE TO SIDE.

13:13.705 --> 13:15.925
[HARMONICA MUSIC]

13:22.758 --> 13:24.281
YEAH, YOU'LL DO.

13:25.108 --> 13:26.806
AND NO MATTER WHAT ANYBODY
SAYS, YOU DON'T ANSWER,

13:26.936 --> 13:28.242
DON'T EVEN STOP PLAYING.

13:28.372 --> 13:30.505
PRETEND LIKE YOU
CAN'T EVEN HEAR 'EM.

13:30.635 --> 13:33.595
-HOBIE: WHY?
-JUST DO IT. DON'T DANCE AROUND
OR ANYTHING. JUST STAND THERE.

13:34.291 --> 13:35.815
GIVE IT A SHOT.

13:37.512 --> 13:39.035
KEEP IT UP.

13:39.644 --> 13:41.298
HI, EXCUSE ME, COULD YOU SPARE

13:41.429 --> 13:43.039
A LITTLE CHANGE FOR
ME AND MY BROTHER?

13:44.562 --> 13:45.955
HI, COULD YOU...

13:47.087 --> 13:48.523
-IT WAS AWFUL, I HATED IT.

13:48.653 --> 13:50.481
-WELL YOU PICKED THE
PLACE, YOU ALWAYS DO.

13:50.612 --> 13:52.179
-LADIES.
-I THOUGHT IT WAS
A GREAT PLACE.

13:52.309 --> 13:55.008
-HI, MY BROTHER AND I,

13:55.138 --> 13:57.619
WE REALLY NEED SOME MONEY,
COULD YOU HELP US OUT?

13:57.749 --> 13:59.186
-WHAT'S WRONG WITH THE BOY?

14:00.230 --> 14:02.015
SEE, HE CAN'T PLAY
TOO WELL, HE'S DEAF.

14:02.145 --> 14:04.582
OH, THANKS WE'RE SAVING
UP FOR A HEARING AID.

14:04.713 --> 14:05.975
WE'RE VERY GRATEFUL.

14:06.106 --> 14:07.759
-BYE.
-THANKS. BYE.

14:10.371 --> 14:12.721
HI.
-HI.

14:12.852 --> 14:14.636
HI, MY BROTHER AND I ARE
TRYING TO GET SOME MONEY

14:14.766 --> 14:17.334
FOR THE BUS HOME, DO YOU
THINK YOU COULD HELP US OUT?

14:17.465 --> 14:18.770
-HOBIE?

14:21.991 --> 14:24.211
-HE CAN'T HEAR
YOU, SEE HE'S DEAF.

14:25.038 --> 14:26.387
-HOBIE.

14:30.826 --> 14:31.914
-YOU SCARED HIM.

14:32.567 --> 14:34.569
HEY, WAIT UP!

14:34.699 --> 14:37.311
-HE CAN'T HEAR YOU, REMEMBER?

14:42.229 --> 14:44.622
-MITCH: GIRL, HUH?
-YEAH.

14:44.753 --> 14:46.624
SHE'S REALLY DIFFERENT, DAD.

14:46.755 --> 14:48.278
-HOW'S SHE DIFFERENT?

14:48.844 --> 14:50.890
WELL, SHE'S OLDER.

14:52.239 --> 14:54.894
I DON'T KNOW, I FEEL
FUNNY AROUND HER.

14:55.503 --> 14:57.113
-FUNNY, HOW?

14:59.376 --> 15:02.031
-WELL, I CAN'T THINK
OF ANYTHING TO SAY,

15:02.684 --> 15:05.121
AND EVERYTHING I DO
SAY SOUNDS STUPID.

15:05.992 --> 15:07.819
-YEAH, WELL, WOMEN CAN DO
THAT TO YOU, BELIEVE ME.

15:11.388 --> 15:12.259
-WHY DOES IT HAPPEN?

15:12.912 --> 15:16.785
-WELL, BECAUSE MAYBE
YOU'RE SAYING ONE THING

15:17.655 --> 15:18.700
AND YOU'RE THINKING
SOMETHING ELSE.

15:19.440 --> 15:23.270
-YEAH, I KEPT ON THINKING
ABOUT KISSING HER.

15:26.926 --> 15:27.839
-WHAT?

15:28.449 --> 15:29.972
-AM I OLD ENOUGH
TO KISS A GIRL, DAD?

15:32.757 --> 15:35.630
-WELL, I, I, UH...

15:35.760 --> 15:37.501
-LOOK, IF YOU DON'T
WANNA TALK ABOUT THIS...

15:37.632 --> 15:39.851
-NO, NO, I DO WANNA
TALK ABOUT THIS.

15:39.982 --> 15:41.418
-THEN WHY ARE YOU
HEMMING AND HAWING?

15:41.549 --> 15:43.029
-I'M...

15:44.508 --> 15:46.075
WELL, BECAUSE IT'S A
LITTLE BIT TOO LATE

15:46.206 --> 15:48.904
TO GET INTO THIS
NOW, AND I DON'T

15:49.035 --> 15:49.992
WANNA HAVE TO STOP
IN THE MIDDLE.

15:51.037 --> 15:52.995
-YEAH, THAT'D PROBABLY
DRIVE ME CRAZY.

15:53.126 --> 15:56.042
-YEAH, I'LL TELL YOU WHAT.

15:56.912 --> 15:58.566
WHY DON'T YOU GO UPSTAIRS,
I'LL TUCK YOU IN BED,

15:58.696 --> 16:00.089
AND WE'LL GET INTO IT TOMORROW.

16:00.220 --> 16:03.875
-GOOD, 'CAUSE THE
STUFF HARVEY TOLD ME

16:04.006 --> 16:04.964
DIDN'T MAKE ANY SENSE.

16:05.094 --> 16:09.316
[GENTLE MUSIC]

18:03.908 --> 18:09.305
[EERIE MUSIC]

18:30.500 --> 18:36.027
[EERIE MUSIC]

19:06.928 --> 19:09.626
-NOT QUITE, THE EYES
ARE STILL TOO CLOSE.

19:09.757 --> 19:11.324
THEY NEED TO BE A
LITTLE, I DON'T KNOW,

19:11.454 --> 19:12.760
DEEPER SET OR SOMETHING.

19:12.890 --> 19:14.501
-HEY GUYS, MITCH AROUND?

19:14.631 --> 19:16.198
-UPSTAIRS.

19:16.329 --> 19:17.852
-WHAT'S THIS?

19:17.982 --> 19:19.941
-SOME CREEP WHO STABBED
ME AT MY TOWER YESTERDAY.

19:20.071 --> 19:20.898
-YOU'RE KIDDING.

19:21.029 --> 19:22.291
-AH, HEY, EDDIE.

19:22.422 --> 19:23.901
SPEAKING OF THE
HOMELESS, DO YOU THINK

19:24.032 --> 19:26.077
I COULD MAYBE STAY WITH
YOU FOR A COUPLE A DAYS?

19:26.208 --> 19:28.210
I MEAN JUST 'TIL I
FIND A SUITABLE PLACE.

19:28.993 --> 19:31.170
-AH COME ON, HARV, YOU KNOW HOW
THE MARINA FEELS ABOUT PETS.

19:32.562 --> 19:34.956
NO, I'M A LITTLE
CRAMPED, YOU UNDERSTAND.

19:35.696 --> 19:37.959
-GARNER, MY MAIN MAN!

19:38.960 --> 19:41.397
-REEVA DOESN'T EVEN LIKE
IT WHEN MY RELATIVES VISIT.

19:41.528 --> 19:42.442
-KAY?

19:43.965 --> 19:45.662
-FORGET IT.

19:46.881 --> 19:48.361
-WAIT A MINUTE, THAT'S IT!

19:48.491 --> 19:50.406
THAT'S IT, NOW YOU'RE
GETTING SOMEWHERE.

19:50.537 --> 19:52.103
-YOU KNOW, GARNER,
I CAN RUN THIS PICTURE

19:52.234 --> 19:53.714
IN "THE VOICE"
