"I SOMETIMES WISH I HAD A SHELL
THAT I COULD CALL MY OWN.

40:41.917 --> 40:43.441
"THEN I WOULDN'T BE ASHAMED

40:43.571 --> 40:45.486
"WHEN SOMEONE ASKS
ME WHERE I LIVED.

40:46.966 --> 40:52.145
"'CAUSE I'D ALWAYS AND
FOREVER, HAVE A HOME."

40:54.016 --> 40:55.017
-THAT WAS BEAUTIFUL, CHARLIE.

40:56.802 --> 40:58.543
-MY MOM'S A REALLY GOOD WRITER.

40:58.673 --> 41:01.023
-I'D LOVE TO PUBLISH SOME OF
WHAT YOU BOTH HAVE WRITTEN.

41:01.154 --> 41:02.634
IF THAT'D BE ALRIGHT.

41:02.764 --> 41:03.983
-IT'S VERY PERSONAL.

41:04.113 --> 41:05.506
-ALL GOOD WRITING IS.

41:05.637 --> 41:06.812
-WILL THEY GET PAID?

41:06.942 --> 41:09.249
-YOU BET, IN FACT,

41:09.379 --> 41:11.556
I COULD USE SOME EXTRA
HELP ON THE PAPER.

41:11.686 --> 41:13.253
-REALLY?

41:13.383 --> 41:14.602
THAT'D BE WONDERFUL.

41:14.733 --> 41:16.517
[DOORBELL RINGING]

41:20.913 --> 41:22.349
-WAIT A MINUTE.

41:22.480 --> 41:23.959
-OH, DON'T WORRY, I'M
NOT LOOKING TO MOVE IN.

41:24.090 --> 41:25.134
I FOUND A PLACE TO ROOST.

41:25.265 --> 41:26.614
-I FEEL SORRY FOR THE CHICKEN.

41:26.745 --> 41:28.660
-HEY, I MOVE IN MONDAY.

41:28.790 --> 41:30.966
32 UNITS, ALL STEWARDESSES.

41:31.576 --> 41:33.012
-I THOUGHT YOU WERE BROKE.

41:33.142 --> 41:35.231
-ROOMMATES, THE SECRET
TO LUXURIOUS LIVING.

41:35.362 --> 41:37.451
-YOU HAVE STEWARDESSES
FOR ROOMMATES?

41:37.582 --> 41:39.845
-WELL, NOT EXACTLY.

41:39.975 --> 41:41.760
YOU SEE, THE DEAL IS
THAT I GET TO MOVE

41:41.890 --> 41:44.197
INTO THEIR APARTMENTS WHEN
THEY'RE AWAY ON FLIGHTS.

41:44.327 --> 41:46.547
BUT, DEALS ARE NEGOTIABLE.

41:47.200 --> 41:48.549
OOH, CAKE.

41:49.637 --> 41:50.464
-COME ON IN.

41:50.595 --> 41:51.639
-HERE YOU GO.

41:51.770 --> 41:53.467
-THANKS.

41:53.598 --> 41:55.600
I DON'T KNOW HOW I'D HAVE
GOTTEN THROUGH THIS WITHOUT YOU.

41:59.081 --> 42:01.083
-DAD, DAD, SHE KISSED ME.

42:01.214 --> 42:02.476
WHAT DO I DO NOW?

42:02.607 --> 42:03.999
-YOU WANT ME TO
HANDLE THIS ONE, MITCH?

42:04.565 --> 42:06.306
-BOOK A FLIGHT, HARVEY.

42:07.002 --> 42:08.134
-OKAY.

42:09.309 --> 42:12.355
-HOBE, A KISS IS LIKE A WAVE.

42:12.486 --> 42:14.880
CATCH THE RIGHT
ONE, UNBELIEVABLE.

42:15.010 --> 42:17.099
CATCH THE WRONG ONE, WIPE-OUT.

42:21.103 --> 42:22.583
-HOW DO YOU TELL
THE DIFFERENCE?

42:22.714 --> 42:24.237
-WELL, WHEN THE WAVES
ARE OVER YOUR HEAD...

42:24.367 --> 42:25.238
-YEAH?

42:25.368 --> 42:26.805
-STAY OUT OF THE WATER.

42:29.590 --> 42:30.460
-HARVEY!

42:33.246 --> 42:38.338
[END THEME PLAYING]
